	(text "AUDIT PAGE: full CH1 signal chain on this page - +5V > CRD D1 > R_ref R1 (V_ref taps CH1_TOP/CH1_MID > U1 ADS1115 AIN0/AIN1) > RTD J1 (Kelvin: Force via loop, Sense pair > J4 > T7) > GND.\nCH2-CH4 (pages 2-4) are identical unit cells; TOP/MID taps land on U1 AIN2/3 (CH2), U2 AIN0/1 (CH3), U2 AIN2/3 (CH4); Sense pairs land on J4 (CH4 on pins 9/10) by the CHn_* labels.\nACCEPTED DEVIATION: CH2-CH4 are separate copies - a unit-cell change must be applied to CH1 (this page) AND pages 2-4 by hand. See docs/sessions/trackE.md."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30.48 220.98 0)
		(effects (font (size 2 2)) (justify left top))
		(uuid "db01977f-b3b6-4a43-bb36-e49aabe4d66e")
	)
